      <title>土耳其通胀率飙升近 70%，且已达峰值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-03/turkey-s-inflation-is-spiraling-closer-to-70-with-rates-at-peak</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其的年度通胀率可能升至 15 个月来的高点，这一增速受到央行的密切关注，该央行在结束加息后仍保持警惕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-03/turkey-s-inflation-is-spiraling-closer-to-70-with-rates-at-peak</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
