      <title>普拉达 (Prada) 乘着奢侈品热潮而大众零售商因中国需求疲软而苦苦挣扎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/prada-rides-luxury-boom-while-mass-retailers-struggle-as-chinese-demand-flags</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Prada SpA 应该在报告财报时确认亚洲奢侈品牌需求的弹性，摆脱中国消费者情绪冷淡的影响。]]></description>
